    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but i've been reading a lot about how it's actually a pretty critical part of the plan to hit climate goals and clean up the city air. is there basically a consensus among urban planners that it's one of the best ways to deal with the environmental stuff?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
