  "judgment": {
    "summary": "The user inquires about the debates surrounding congestion pricing in NYC, specifically asking about environmental consensus and equity concerns. The assistant provides a balanced overview of the pros (climate/traffic) and cons (equity/burden on low-income residents) before addressing how planners attempt to mitigate those equity concerns through revenue recycling.",
